{1: '1', 2: 'Kiske', 3: '【kuroname】, hey there.', 4: '1'}

{2: "Uh... I think I'll pass.", 3: '18'}
{2: 'Kiske', 3: 'What a shame. This is my pride and joy.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Child Vendor', 3: 'Hi there! Care to give this a try?', 4: '1'}
{2: "Sure, I'll have some.", 3: '28', 4: 'No, thanks.', 5: '29'}
{2: 'Child Vendor', 3: 'Thank you. Just a moment.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Child Vendor', 3: 'Alright, just drop by whenever you have time.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami, what are you up to...?', 3: '37', 4: 'I see you, Nanami!', 5: '37'}
{2: "It's impossible not to notice you.", 3: '40'}
{2: 'You whisper "snap" to yourself every single time.', 3: '42'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hehehe!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "I had Zavier make this camera for me, but there's no shutter sound at all.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'It\'s got to go "snaap!" when you take a photo, or it\'s just not fun!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'That totally makes sense.', 3: '49', 4: "There's no way that's a real thing, right?", 5: '50'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'I knew you would get it, Commandant!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "What? It's not?!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'But Nanami, why are you taking pictures of me?', 3: '53'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Because I want to capture exactly how you look, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Then I'm putting it all together into a big, thick photo album!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'This way, I can see you anytime I want!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'You know, you can always just come directly to me.', 3: '59'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Heh heh, I know!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'But I want to film your everyday life—how you hang out and connect with everyone else.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "I figure the only way to capture the real you is when you have no idea I'm recording.", 4: '1'}
{2: "From one perspective, you're taking photos without consent.", 3: '64', 4: 'I guess that makes some sense...', 5: '66'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Sorry about that, Commandant!', 4: '1'}
{2: "Mind if I check out the photos you've taken?", 3: '69'}
{3: 'Nanami extends her hand and shows you the camera.'}
{3: "You flip through the photos on the camera: they show everything from you sitting on a plaza bench to you saying hi to people... there's even a shot of you playing with a kitten."}
{3: 'And from a certain angle, the pictures Nanami took actually look pretty good...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'So, what do you think? They came out great, right?', 4: '1'}
{2: "Why don't we snap a few group photos too?", 3: '77'}
{2: 'They might be even more meaningful that way.', 3: '78'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Yeah, sounds good!', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory783.jpg'}
{3: 'The sun gradually sets, painting the distant sky a deep red.'}
{3: "Nanami, having just left the human's company, sits on a bench with a photo album in her hands."}
{3: 'A fleeting moment in time is carefully cut out and kept safe.'}
{3: "She slowly turns the pages of the album, her eyes resting on a group picture, but it feels as if she's looking all the way into the future."}
{3: 'In the photo, she and 【kuroname】 each hold an ice cream cone, forming peace signs with free hands, smiling straight into the camera.'}
{3: 'Nanami wears a warm, gentle smile on her face.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami likes Commandant so much, more than anything.', 4: '1'}
